title: v2.0: ccp_showNameCode value should be inverted
message:
v2.0: ccp_showNameCode value should be inverted

Looks like you renamed `hideNameCode` to `ccp_showNameCode` [(ref)](https://github.com/hbb20/CountryCodePickerProject/wiki/Update-Guide-for-v2.0.0) and you forgot to invert the boolean value in the code.

When using `app:ccp_showNameCode="false"`, the name code is shown, but when using `app:ccp_showNameCode="true"`, the name code is not shown.
